articles.title: About me
articles.contents:
Kevin is a student at the Univerisity of Toronto. He hopes to get into the Data Science program but perhaps his grades are too low.
His most notable achievement in life is probably getting an 80 in ENV200.
He occasionally programs and hopes to have a job one day.
